QuestData.Title: A Spirit's Duty
QuestData.Description:
I seek to understand more about the Dutiful beings in this realm.
If you could place one in a wildseed, as you did for me, I could observe the restoration process.
QuestData.LogDescription: Place a Dutiful Spirit into a wildseed.

Objectives.Objective: Place a Dutiful Spirit in a Wildseed
